Strata-management company:A strata-management company is a company that manages and maintains common property in a strata scheme, such as apartment buildings or townhouses.
Low-power and high-power air conditioners:Low-power and high-power air conditioners refer to air conditioning units with different cooling capacities and energy consumption levels.
Total number of air conditioners:The total number of air conditioners refers to the combined quantity of low-power and high-power models that need to be purchased to meet the cooling requirements of the housing units.
